reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 15, 2021
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Great diaper, Needs Stretchy Sides!
reviews.reviewText: The size of this diaper is great for a size 7. The only problem is the sides have very little stretch, limiting them to very skinny children. If anyone from Sleepys is reading this, please make the sides more stretchy. Pampers shouldn't have a monopoly on stretchy diapers.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on June 8, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 2.0 out of 5 stars Not transparent on ingredients
reviews.reviewText: It says no perfumes but you can definitely smell some sort of fragrance from the diapers which makes me wonder what other ingredients are in these diapers that they didn’t mention on description. Wouldn’t trust it if you baby has sensitive skin.
